            <title>[DERBY-6179] Insert some guarding code into the first replication test to check port availability</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6179</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have seen lots of noise in the nightlies with replication failing. It seems that often it fails due to ports being unavailable, possibly due to earlier (failed) runs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This JIRA issue tracks diagnostic code I want to insert to see what&apos;s happening at test run time.&lt;br/&gt;
The diagnostic code can be removed when we have stabilized the tests.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
